cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep reinforcement learning and the convergence of neural network-based algorithms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the optimization of policies, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the use of overparametrized neural networks is a key aspect of the paper, which is relevant to the field of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
